Quarterly commentary  



Total returns details  






People and process

Firms
Vanguard Fixed Income Group
Product management
Vanguard Pennsylvania Municipal Money Market Fund seeks to provide current income that is exempt from federal and state income taxes, while maintaining a stable $1 NAV and a very short average maturity. The fund invests in high-quality, short-term Pennsylvania municipal securities. The fund maintains a dollar-weighted average maturity of 60 days or less, and a dollar-weighted average life of 120 days or less.
Firm and manager details  





